ref: Jour: Yadernaya Fizika, Vol.19, Issue.4, p.715 (1974)
title: Investigation of Level Density for Some Nuclei of Sd Shell By Means of The Energy Spectra of The (N,P) Reactions At The Neutron Energy of 14.1 Mev

x4codes.hlp: Leningradskii Tekhnologicheskii Inst. Im.Lensoveta, Union of Soviet Socialist Republics

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Yadernaya Fizika, Vol.19, Issue.4, p.715 (1974)

x4freetext: DATA  AND SOME GRAPHS ARE GIVEN
INVESTIGATION OF LEVEL DENSITY FOR SOME NUCLEI OF SD
SHELL BY MEANS OF THE ENERGY SPECTRA OF THE (N,P)
REACTIONS AT THE NEUTRON ENERGY OF 14.1 MEV
COUNTER TELESCOPE CONSISTS OF THREE PROPORTIONAL
COUNTERS. ENERGY AND ANGULAR RESOLUTION WAS 400 KEV AND
LEAST-SQUARE METHOD AND STATISTICAL THEORY OF NUCLEAR
REACTIONS FOR FERMI-GAS MODEL AND SUPPER-CONTACTIVE
CROSS SECTION OF THE INVERSE REACTION WAS USED FROM
CORRECTION FOR MISCALCULATION OF THE ANALYZER,ENERGY
LOSSES OF THE PARTICLES,BACKGROUND WERE TAKEN INTO
